### Running Tests

```bash
# Run tests
pytest

# Run tests with coverage
pytest --cov=laneful

# Run type checking
mypy laneful/

# Run linting
ruff check laneful/
black --check laneful/
```

### Code Formatting

```bash
# Format code
black laneful/ tests/
isort laneful/ tests/

# Check formatting
ruff check laneful/
```

